This post is dedicated to all the cakes I made that were not posted in 2022! Admittedly, this ever changing algorithm and low visibility had me feeling super unmotivated. Or I wouldn’t post a cake because it didn’t go with the aesthetic of my profile at the time (smh). 

But with that all being said, I am always forever grateful for those of you that are still seeing my content and showing support! So for that, I will work on sharing some more and hope I don’t end the year with a portfolio of cakes that can almost fill up the names of this DMX challenge again! 🥴😂
